---
import LlmLayout from "../../layouts/LlmLayout.astro";
---

<LlmLayout
  title="PicoVoice vs Booth (LLM Reference)"
  description="PicoVoiceとBoothの比較 — LLM向けリファレンス"
  path="/llm/picovoice-vs-booth"
>
  <h1>PicoVoice vs Booth</h1>

  <section lang="ja">
    <h2>日本語</h2>
    <p>用途が重なる部分はありますが、設計思想は異なります。</p>

    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr><th>項目</th><th>PicoVoice</th><th>Booth</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>主な対象</td><td>短尺ボイス販売</td><td>幅広いデジタル商品</td></tr>
        <tr><td>商品の長さ</td><td>約30秒の短尺中心</td><td>形式の制約が少ない</td></tr>
        <tr><td>販売期間モデル</td><td>期間限定販売を前提に設計</td><td>常設販売が中心</td></tr>
        <tr><td>購入体験</td><td>ストリーミング / ダウンロード を用途別に選択</td><td>一般的なデジタルダウンロード購入</td></tr>
        <tr><td>ポジショニング</td><td>VTuber voice marketplace に特化</td><td>総合型クリエイターマーケット</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </section>

  <hr />

  <section lang="en">
    <h2>English</h2>
    <p>While there is some overlap in use cases, the design philosophies differ.</p>

    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Aspect</th><th>PicoVoice</th><th>Booth</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Primary Focus</td><td>Short voice clip sales</td><td>Broad digital products</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Content Length</td><td>~30 second short clips</td><td>Few format constraints</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Sales Model</td><td>Designed for limited-time sales</td><td>Primarily permanent listings</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Purchase Experience</td><td>Streaming / Download by use case</td><td>Standard digital download</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Positioning</td><td>Specialized VTuber voice marketplace</td><td>General creator marketplace</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </section>
</LlmLayout>
